<br>
Several months ago, I was running through West Freeport.  I normally do not watch OOC or shout in the city, but a comment in OOC caught my eye.  Basically, a player was trying to defend their behavior because they didn't have all their spells yet.  I scrolled up and found a few other people in the zone getting on the player case because of the 'poor' way they were taking down mobs and then looting the corpses.  This player said they were saving up to buy the rest of their level 1 spells.<br>
<br>
I was nearly to the North Freeport zone, but I stopped and did a quick /who to see the person was a level 2 Enchanter.  I sent them a tell, asking them to meet me just inside the city gates.  Up walks a DE female and I hand her 5pp and say something to the effect of, &quot;Go get the rest of your spells.&quot;  She emotes a blink, happy, and thanks me.  I throw a few buffs on her and run off to North Freeport.<br>
<br>
It turns out I knew her primary from one of the boards I frequented at the time.  We started talking and developed a friendship from that point on.  Helping someone I already knew was serendipity.  Helping someone trying to play the designed system was not and it felt good to do it. <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#3A6EA5">Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;Final Destiny&gt;</B></FONT><BR>
<I><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#cfcfcf">Ranger of Karana</I></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ucrydeeossiriand.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Crydee Ossiriand</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(2/15/01 5:39:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=171.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /rude EZboard</span><hr size=1> I really wish Verant would make this item real, but they'd have to make it so that the item would become glued to your character & couldn't be removed...<br>
